promptPrefix:
Improve the quality of the following content by proofreading, adding the most relevant factually correct information, and keeping it reading level of 5th grade with a first person friendly tone of voice. Try to sound like a human writer. Also, try to sound unique and write in an unpredictable fashion that doesn't like GPT3. Avoid writing generic words, jargon words, and generic keyphrases. Don't start with a question. Must have contractions in writing. All output will be [TARGETLANGUAGE] 
[PROMPT]
title: Expend Content Like 100% Human Written (V.2)
